==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stainless
<hw>Stain"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from stain;
immaculate.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The very care he took to keep his name⟦br⟧
<qex>Stainless</qex>, with some was evidence of shame.</q>
<rj><qau>Crabbe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Blameless; spotless; faultless. See
<er>Blameless</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stainlessly</ent>⟦br⟧
